data.text: New gong mallet on left. Two views of old mallet- note the screws! #nofoolin #livebv

Yeah, its amazing what a shift in role can do to your #productivity. #livebv pic.twitter.com/dqHAZn5017
That's a wrap on a b:allin April Fools Day. My coworkers really know how to stick it to the (wo)man #livebv
Beautiful double rainbow on this rainy Friday morning. #livebv
Henri bringing the fun to Fridays at BV. #livebv
Dustin, you've been replaced. No hard feelings? #BVNYC #livebv #nyc #Manhattan
Here comes trouble to #BVNYC . Love when BV alumnus come back for a visit. #nyc #Manhattan #livebv
@chrisolfers taking a photo of a happy rainbow at work. #livebv

View from my office. Happy Friday. #livebv

Whole Foods Market Express opened in our office today. Cold section, hot bar, salad bar, pastries, and coffee. #livebv
Whole foods is about to break this bread inside of BV! #livebv
@wholefoods Cafe now open at @bazaarvoice.  This will be dangerous.  #tacoseveryday #livebv
